,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T04:14:56.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T04:19:55.000Z","msg":"最近個次旺角 最新的"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T04:20:33.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T04:33:00.000Z","msg":"阿叔手足戴番個口罩先啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c92333d389dbfc9771640a1d4fc32141cd4ec86","tid":1927802,"uid":286897,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T04:37:09.000Z","msg":"【攻略】光復功能組別強化策略 (3月起啟用)<br />\n<br />\n✅全民 &gt; 組社團 + 組工會 + 開公司<br />\n✅專業人士 &gt; 登記專業界別<br />\n✅本身有BR &gt; 直接登記商界<br />\n✅手足 &gt; 掃黃店<br />\n<br />\n🔺組工會 (勞工界)<br />\n- 已確認核實，即使工會審批時間長短<br />\n- 只要你5月2日前提交申請, 就可以趕及2021特首選委🔥<br />\n組隊神器 7起 &gt; <a href=\"https://7up.hkpetitions.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2F7up.hkpetitions.com&d=ly5XvLwGuIZ6JSW2uqe%2Bvv3ZlJXgeXtiTXALECG4O5Q%3D&h=b1259fb0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://7up.hkpetitions.com</a><br />\n無敵Q&amp;A &gt; <a href=\"https://electionboost.blogspot.com/2020/01/blog-post_12.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Felectionboost.blogspot.com%2F2020%2F01%2Fblog-post_12.html&d=ly5XvLwGuIZ6JSW2uqe%2Bvv3ZlJXgeXtiTXALECG4O5Q%3D&h=9fa83832\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://electionboost.blogspot.com/2020/01/blog-post_12.html</a><br />\n<br />\n🔺開公司 (萬能界)<br />\n- 帶身份證去灣仔税局搞，俾$250，30分鐘搞掂 @businessfrontier<br />\n- 輕量級 &gt; 紡織界 $61/ 體育界 $2000/ 出版界 $1140 (撳個掣就得)<br />\n- 重量級 &gt; 商界 $3900/ 工業界 $2970/ 零售界 $1180/ 僱主聯合會 $4800<br />\n- 集中首選 &gt; 進出口界 $240+1320 (1年以上BR+商業地址）<br />\n<a href=\"https://electionboost.blogspot.com/2020/03/blog-post_57.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Felectionboost.blogspot.com%2F2020%2F03%2Fblog-post_57.html&d=ly5XvLwGuIZ6JSW2uqe%2Bvv3ZlJXgeXtiTXALECG4O5Q%3D&h=d16735ed\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://electionboost.blogspot.com/2020/03/blog-post_57.html</a><br />\n<br />\n🔺申請進出口牌 (進出口界）<br />\n只要有一年以上BR同埋商業地址，唔理你做咩生意，都可以向海關申請進出口牌，立即成為進出口界公司選民<br />\nTelegram: <a href=\"http://t.me/exportfrontier\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fexportfrontier&d=ly5XvLwGuIZ6JSW2uqe%2Bvv3ZlJXgeXtiTXALECG4O5Q%3D&h=f47768b0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/exportfrontier</a><br />\nFacebook: <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/exportfrontier/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fexportfrontier%2F&d=ly5XvLwGuIZ6JSW2uqe%2Bvv3ZlJXgeXtiTXALECG4O5Q%3D&h=7f0d8564\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/exportfrontier/</a><br />\n<br />\n🔺掃黃店 (飲食界、零售界)<br />\n組隊幫手登記 &gt; <a href=\"https://forms.gle/am8LThtTL9r6joL17\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforms.gle%2Fam8LThtTL9r6joL17&d=ly5XvLwGuIZ6JSW2uqe%2Bvv3ZlJXgeXtiTXALECG4O5Q%3D&h=b5057862\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://forms.gle/am8LThtTL9r6joL17</a><br />\n掃黃店進度表 &gt; <a href=\"https://bit.ly/3cEJGz6\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F3cEJGz6&d=ly5XvLwGuIZ6JSW2uqe%2Bvv3ZlJXgeXtiTXALECG4O5Q%3D&h=617ccd64\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/3cEJGz6</a><br />\n黃店名單 &gt; <a href=\"https://www.hkshoplist.com/select.php\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkshoplist.com%2Fselect.php&d=ly5XvLwGuIZ6JSW2uqe%2Bvv3ZlJXgeXtiTXALECG4O5Q%3D&h=f8e843a4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hkshoplist.com/select.php</a><br />\n<br />\n🔺組社團 (文化界)<br />\n1. 齊集三人，須有相關文化資歷證明<br />\n2. 準備社團資料 - 宗旨/ 規章/ 擬辦活動<br />\n3. 準備個人資料 - 身分證副本/ 住址+會址證明 (3個月內)(銀行/水電煤單據)<br />\n4. 約組員出黎，互簽名，互交換文件<br />\n5. 寄出去 /親身交到警總 Done!<br />\n<a href=\"https://electionboost.blogspot.com/2020/01/blog-post_33.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Felectionboost.blogspot.com%2F2020%2F01%2Fblog-post_33.html&d=ly5XvLwGuIZ6JSW2uqe%2Bvv3ZlJXgeXtiTXALECG4O5Q%3D&h=da0af7a4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://electionboost.blogspot.com/2020/01/blog-post_33.html</a><br />\n<br />\n🔺每個香港人都可以拎三票<br />\n1. 地區個人票 (地方選區有得投）<br />\n2. 功能組別個人票 (正常人係超區)<br />\n3. 功能組別團體票(不可跟2同一界別)<br />\n<br />\n例子, 地方選區：香港島/ 功能界別(個人票)：超級區議會/ 功能界別(團體票)：飲食界<br />\n<a href=\"https://electionboost.blogspot.com/2020/01/blog-post_57.html?m=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Felectionboost.blogspot.com%2F2020%2F01%2Fblog-post_57.html%3Fm%3D1&d=ly5XvLwGuIZ6JSW2uqe%2Bvv3ZlJXgeXtiTXALECG4O5Q%3D&h=e75f9cd3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://electionboost.blogspot.com/2020/01/blog-post_57.html?m=1</a><br />\n<br />\n重點功能界別的whatapps Hotline<br />\nGeneral whatapps Hotline : 65391922<br />\n 體演文出whatapps Hotline : 66700860<br />\n 進出口界whatapps Hotline : 68461562<br />\n 飲食界whatapps Hotline : 9180 3949 / 66812202<br />\n 批發及零售whatapps Hotline : 65391922<br />\n<br />\n📣 請訂閱作戰研究院 Telegram Channel ➼ @FightResearch<br />\n戰術研究 | 抗爭資訊 | 時局分析 | 評論 | 趣事<br />\nCredits to 七起"},{"pid":"89f58c152d656feb22a1f7b836dfa8bf891b6520","tid":1927802,"uid":37413,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T04:42:31.000Z","msg":"警刷都好大壓力，要包容"},{"pid":"f3a662d9ae5b3c64e7f86542a463d33eacac7bee","tid":1927802,"uid":173844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T04:44:27.000Z","msg":"班仆街咁啱冇拎住支胡椒噴霧又懶得拎出黎姐<br />\n不過阿叔不畏黑警又識分黑白係勁嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f22d05513bcf6ecc1fbaacd3a7767dc3e0f56633","tid":1927802,"uid":222970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T05:46:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f2ce5416c3ff1d7adae3e87a09b096f1a3e1999","tid":1927802,"uid":306681,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T10:26:50.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b90cfc1564dfe5a35a1f6ee91fb2a2d6ecfa9ab7","tid":1927802,"uid":11454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0f2ce5416c3ff1d7ada